{"tid":1702600,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【求救】間房度牆有隻不知名觸手生物 (慎入)","createTime":"2019-11-09T18:53:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T02:05:37.000Z","uid":57186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2340c8a6ee947224cc55c745795bd30d9a15dbbd","tid":1702600,"uid":57186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T18:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/teB5pua.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FteB5pua.jpg&h=60f88cdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/35JrTnx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F35JrTnx.jpg&h=bfaec909&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4JwXZ2D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4JwXZ2D.jpg&h=f19fee22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開頭以為乜有舊塵痴左係牆，拎紙巾想執走佢<br />\n點知行近少少直覺話俾我聽唔對路，塵唔似塵，蟲唔似蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n企係到觀察一陣，見到佢慢慢伸出隻觸手/賓周係到搖來搖去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嚇到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解會咁D咁既野係我間房出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無生物學巴打/動物博士知道呢隻係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我相信係某種蟲既幼年期，好想知佢完全體係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"503a528163214201501179e5487823c39f7aba66","tid":1702600,"uid":235277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T18:55:34.000Z","msg":"依蛾<br />\n<br />\n潮濕引起"},{"pid":"95bf9cb7a59a9eab892f5e2d1ed91c673f1c2ab4","tid":1702600,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T18:56:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=%E8%A1%A3%E8%9B%BE&amp;sxsrf=ACYBGNQG6KD4cZzTdCmbux58bkGFZ_cLAw:1573325749359&amp;source=lnms&amp;tbm=isch&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwjP_Z-T593lAhXNh3AKHTRgBaUQ_AUIEigB&amp;biw=1920&amp;bih=937\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E8%259B%25BE%26sxsrf%3DACYBGNQG6KD4cZzTdCmbux58bkGFZ_cLAw%3A1573325749359%26source%3Dlnms%26tbm%3Disch%26sa%3DX%26ved%3D0ahUKEwjP_Z-T593lAhXNh3AKHTRgBaUQ_AUIEigB%26biw%3D1920%26bih%3D937&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpj%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=5f50ffc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/search?q=%E8%A1%A3%E8%9B%BE&amp;sxsrf=ACYBGNQG6KD4cZzTdCmbux58bkGFZ_cLAw:1573325749359&amp;source=lnms&amp;tbm=isch&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwjP_Z-T593lAhXNh3AKHTRgBaUQ_AUIEigB&amp;biw=1920&amp;bih=937</a>"},{"pid":"edf4d557d8283e75f7b5087aac69cd6e42b5efe3","tid":1702600,"uid":167721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T18:56:04.000Z","msg":"之前睇過記得唔係害蟲<br />\n不過都係津路水炮啦"},{"pid":"a6fc349e9bbc29dc5690f91343cf96c9a579f9f8","tid":1702600,"uid":57186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T18:57:28.000Z","msg":"另外，牆上呢排仲有一隻二隻同蚊差唔多大，<br />\n全黑色，無手腳伸出來，幼長型啲<br />\n就痴係牆你唔搞佢都唔郁既(近兩日都無出現，影唔到相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 開頭以為咩衣魚，google左又唔同樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家每次都好驚望度牆，唔知又會有乜出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im